- No, all you.

48:24.318 --> 48:25.611
Sweet.

48:26.862 --> 48:29.614
Oh my God, what a fucking day.

48:29.615 --> 48:33.951
<i>♪ Though I tried not to hurt you,
though I tried ♪</i>

48:33.952 --> 48:36.913
Not a holiday for me, man.
I can tell you that much.

48:36.914 --> 48:39.082
-  Throw it to me. Throw it to me!
-  Alright, go.

48:40.417 --> 48:42.668
- Let's go!
- Yeah! Superman!

48:45.380 --> 48:49.843
I did get to give Presley
some good advice though on that.

48:51.386 --> 48:53.930
It just feels important
'cause she's growing up so...

